    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> ciabatta[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Spread the <strong>cheesy garlic butter</strong> over the outside of the<strong> ciabatta lids</strong> and the inside of the <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>bases</strong>, then add to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5-7 min or until crusty – this is your<strong> garlic bread</strong></p>",
