    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free chick'n </strong>to the pan with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown</p>",
