    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>gem lettuce </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then separate 1 outer leaf per person and cut the <strong>remaining lettuce </strong>into quarters, lengthways</p><p>Combine the <strong>mashed roasted garlic </strong>and <strong>mayo</strong> in a small bowl with your<strong> white wine vinegar</strong> – this is your <strong>roasted garlic aioli</strong></p>",
